dcterms:description: The dataset consists of re-annotated five existing datasets with 68 landmarks: iBug, LFPW, AFW, HELEN and XM2VTS. It is used for training and testing facial landmark detection algorithms.
dcterms:title: 300-W

dcterms:description: AFLW contains a total of 24,386 faces with a large variety in appearance (e.g., pose, expression, ethnicity, and age) and environmental conditions. It provides at most 21 landmarks for each face, with 19 landmarks used for evaluation.
dcterms:title: AFLW
